D,1241,GENL,,,Description,12,,13,,5,Details remarks,49,3
C,A,,,,,ISO Container,,,GENL,,,,DFBU,,,,NZAKL,AUSYD,070182,,,,ZGHH8063770,,2300,,CNAKL,,,,,,MSK,,,,,,,,,,,,,15730
