D,1251,GENL,,,Description,12,,13,,5,Details remarks,49,3
C,U,,,,,ISO Container,,,GENL,,,,DFBU,,,,NZAKL,AUSYD,070384,,,,ZGHH8063778,,2300,,CNAKL,,,,,,MSK,,,,,,,,,,,,,15730
C,U,,,,,ISO Container,,,GENL,,,,DFBU,,,,NZAKL,AUSYD,070484,,,,ZGHH8063779,,2300,,CNAKL,,,,,,MSK,,,,,,,,,,,,,15730
